OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fovernight. Largely clear at first, but
OL,7,Fcloud will tend to thicken bringing
OL,8,Fcloudy conditions for some by dawn.
OL,9,FWinds generally easing across the
OL,10,Fregion and turning chilly, with a
OL,11,Frural frost possible in sheltered
OL,12,Fspots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FCloudy start in places, but
OL,15,Fwidespread sunshine developing through
OL,16,Fthe morning to give a fine day.
OL,17,FFeeling cooler towards the northeast
OL,18,Fcoast, with an onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
